data.description: A 4-bedroom, 3-bath walkout ranch, updated and ready to welcome a new family. Floorplan works well for a multigenerational family, with a large family room, 2 bedrooms, full bath, kitchenette in the sunlit lower level, walkout covered patio. Upstairs living area expanded by covered/screened-in deck. French patio doors have in-glass blinds. Kitchen boasts huge pantry, all upgraded appliances in 2023, recent granite countertops. Pull-out shelves in second pantry and lower cabinets, a pull-down spice rack.  Upstairs floors beautiful white oak floors, basement floor CoreTex luxury vinyl planking. Updated can lights.  3-car garage has LusterStone floor. New roof and vinyl siding with extra insulation 2021. Irrigation system.  ADA features: master bath, ramp access in master, stair chair, elevator. 16 kw Generac. A/C replaced 8/22. Large back yard, vinyl fence, backs to green space. Tankless water heater. So much storage. ALL APPLIANCES INCLUDED!
